title: Welcome To My Blog
text:
First post!
Everything I’ve done in the past has been in private industry, it’s time to step out and put some work in public.
I’ve worked as an industrial food scientist and statistician.
I’ll sometimes talk about how things work, probably more often how they don’t work.
I’ll be adding videos on YouTube, check those out too.
